|text1     = There are some wind currents in the Eye of Twilight. Platforms that pass through them will be pushed by the air currents. {{Color|h|nobold=1|Change the direction of the wind by Rewinding}} the nearby device that can control the wind currents, allowing the platforms to move to the other side. After using the shrine to {{Color|h|nobold=1|enhance prayers, this Rewind process will not have a time limit}}, and remains continuous.
|image2    = Tutorial Wind Currents in Eye of Twilight 2.png{{subst:void|<!--$UPLOAD:<<SpriteOutput/TutorialPic/TutorialPage_635202.png>-<Tutorial Wind Currents in Eye of Twilight 2.png>-<Tutorial Files>>-->}}
|text2     = While a device is Rewinding, {{Color|h|nobold=1|tap the Rewind button again to interrupt the Rewinding, reversing the wind current}}. With this function, stand on the platform, Rewind devices or interrupt their Rewinding to change the direction of the wind, and move to another location with the platform.
